{"tid":2351754,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午+是靚甜","createTime":"2021-01-03T13:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T21:04:10.000Z","uid":376170,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"281f6a3f3c8c24e01b13e567cdaa4c5a12c7c8b9","tid":2351754,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32oLWBX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32oLWBX.png&h=334aa35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和風牛柳粒丼配溫泉蛋飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一上嚟就聞到好香嘅牛同菇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n菇同豆都好入味<br />\n完全冇忽略到配菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MhQixap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhQixap.png&h=04014d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每條薯圈都好大抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mpf6F6r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpf6F6r.png&h=43de570d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即叫即整<br />\n<br />\n鬆軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識震<br />\n每啖都有強烈空氣口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺落口之後啲蛋香衝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有雲呢拿雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c635983278c0e2933e77ce9b6198690262ce9b74","tid":2351754,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"又幾靚咁wor"},{"pid":"beb9acf830f64961f82db29e1f73a6dd5dd05404","tid":2351754,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"未食嘢好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif